  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Provide attentive customer service and support restaurant operations to ensure a clean environment and smooth service flow.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver courteous and helpful customer service to meet guest needs and enhance their dining experience</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene standards throughout the restaurant to ensure a safe and welcoming environment</li><li>Address guest concerns and complaints calmly and effectively to resolve issues promptly</li><li>Collaborate and communicate clearly with team members and management to coordinate service and operational tasks</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of three years of relevant experience in a similar role</li></ul><p>Benefits:</p><ul><li>Annual Leave (AL)</li><li>Medical Leave</li><li>Incentive</li><li>Fixed Sunday Off</li></ul>",
